org.json.stream

Interface StructureCollector<OA,AA,OR,AR>

  • Type Parameters:
    OA - the JSON object accumulator type created by the factory
    AA - the JSON array accumulator type created by the factory
    OR - the JSON object result type
    AR - the JSON array result type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionCollector, JSONCollector

    public interface StructureCollector<OA,AA,OR,AR>
    Allows JSONLimitBuilder to parameterise the creation and population of object and array structures, null values, and creation of a "finished" result type. Similar to Collector in Java 8's stream package.

    For instance, structures may be created as JSONObject and JSONArray, with JSONObject.NULL for JSON null. Another factory may create structures as HashMap and ArrayList, and Java's null value for JSON null.
